EEA holds large amounts of information on Europe\ufffd\ufffd\ufffds environment that is presented in a series of formats:\ufffd\ufffdreports,\ufffd\ufffdindicators,\ufffd\ufffddata sets,\ufffd\ufffdmap-based hourly measurements of ground-level ozone concentrations, web pages, videos, etc.\ufffd\ufffd

You may find it time-consuming to find and be informed of the latest updates of interest to you. Our targeted information service allows you to receive our latest outputs in your areas of interest and in the format of your choice. You can also select to receive our newsletters.

So please sign up and help us improve our dissemination services to match your information needs.

If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us at subscriptions@eea.europa.eu.

\ufffd\ufffd

PLEASE NOTE:\ufffd\ufffdYou are leaving the EEA website and going to a website carrying out dissemination service on behalf of the EEA. Please be advised that this external website provides an additional service that is consistent with the intended purpose of the EEA website and EEA\ufffd\ufffd\ufffds privacy policy.\ufffd\ufffdAll information entered will be treated confidentially, only used for dissemination of EEA material and not made available to third parties. You may cancel your subscription any time you wish.
